| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-6005 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7062c055-f1f3-54e9-a1b6-c40d7a004030"
